4-7 W000000T Pet! Well, this made it a lot easier. I watched someone take the first kobold camp solo, and I decided to try. I was lucky that the spawns were managable. I got up to 6, then logged. When I came back, of course, all 3 kobolds conning blue right there. So, I nuked one, and ran my ass off to Guard Halv(think it was him). When I got back, I summoned air pet, and waited. The one by the fire spawns the quickest, followed by the small tent, then quickly afterwards by the one in the larger tent. Also, there was one kobold off left on a cliff that was nice when I was waiting for another spawn. Quick exp, plus scalps for mage quests <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
